title: Mir Sarfraz Domki, Shakeel Durrani call on PM
content:
ISLAMABAD, Aug 16 (APP):Former Provincial Minister Mir Sarfraz Chakar Domki and Agha Shakeel Durrani called on Caretaker Prime Minister Anwaar-ul-Haq Kakar here on Wednesday.
The two leaders congratulated the Caretaker PM on assuming the office and extended best wishes to him, the PM Office Media Wing said in a press release.
The caretaker prime minister thanked both the leaders for their best wishes.
